{"tid":879813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被強國大媽從碗裡搶錢　身障乞丐無助哭喊","createTime":"2018-10-28T09:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T04:15:32.000Z","uid":121473,"like":328,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"6269efc3e93d59814a47cb6f71c7797de4ea10da","tid":879813,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mENYNJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmENYNJR.jpg&h=c856a46c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國四川遂寧市一名大媽，上周五（26日）在路邊見一名身障乞丐的罐子裡有些錢，便彎下腰，伸手拿走罐子裡的錢，然後快步離開。乞丐因為行動不便，只能坐在地上，不停揮動雙手、叫喊求助。然而，沒有路人願意伸出援手。<br />\n <br />\n監視器拍下，一名穿著紅色衣服的乞丐坐在路邊，身前放著一個行乞用的罐子，向路人乞討。一名背著竹簍的大媽突然走近乞丐，低頭一看罐子裡有錢後，先看了乞丐一會，便伸手到罐裡把錢拿走。<br />\n <br />\n大媽「搶」錢塊步離開，乞丐揮動雙手叫喊，引起3名路過的年輕女子注意，但沒有人願意幫他把大媽攔下。<br />\n <br />\n當地城管表示，已透過監視器掌握情況，會把案件轉交給警方追查。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181028/1455648/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455648%2F&d=ZlWKHdNPxtLZfwSwDXSCp54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cacb53ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181028%2F1455648%2F&h=98fc400c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181028/1455648/</a>"},{"pid":"444fada233d1218309c22a1c7c4b16c618c11766","tid":879813,"uid":218977,"like":341,"dislike":19,"score":322,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52c0f04c784f5273b35f85635d094323abcfe9f7","tid":879813,"uid":18569,"like":25,"dislike":159,"score":-134,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"呢個大媽做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfcc7501346ea4df21856709f0b0257c4efb5c6","tid":879813,"uid":205587,"like":541,"dislike":2,"score":539,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:50:15.000Z",